          "character": "刘封、糜竺",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将与我放箭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、魏延、赵云同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞、魏延、赵云",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周瑜哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同杀。周瑜下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将军请了。军师将令，不放他回去。你我就在江边埋伏。\n来，埋伏者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
