    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "为臣光宠不长久",
        "众人",
        "倘若为臣死之后",
        "周瑜",
        "四将",
        "大骂孔明诡计有",
        "将甲",
        "甘宁",
        "诸葛计策真不透"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜上，吴兵、四将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，俺本当转回南徐，可恨孔明挡住去路，不容俺回都，这便怎处？\n众将官，前面是什么地方？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巴邱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将人马撤回巴邱。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴兵同下。甘宁上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀都督：末将打听孔明与刘备，在山头饮酒取乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明，你好妙计吓。咳。周瑜你好无志量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "屡次兴兵龙虎斗，\n损兵折将面含羞。\n枉费徒劳统貔貅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛计策真不透、甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀都督：诸葛亮差下书人到此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将书呈上，待我拆看：\n“汉军师中郎将诸葛亮，致书于东吴都督周公瑾先生麾下。亮自柴桑一别，至\n今念念不忘。闻足下欲取西川，亮窃以为不可。益州民强地险，刘璋软弱，足\n以自守。今劳师远征，转运万里，欲收全功，管乐不能定其功，孙武不能善其\n后。曹操失利于赤壁，志岂须臾忘报仇哉。今足下兴兵远征，倘曹操乘虚而至，\n江南齑粉矣。亮不忍坐视，特此告知，幸垂临焉。”\n啊呀，气死我也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "气满胸膛噎咽喉，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲜血不住顺口流。\n这封书好一似神鬼钩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大骂孔明诡计有、四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，都督息怒，保全身体要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军，我周瑜今番性命休矣。吾这里寄书回见吴侯，说周瑜不能生回，可\n将兵权印玺付与鲁肃执掌，众将协力报效，自有封妻荫子之日，共成大业。敢\n烦甘将军，与吾带书叩见吴侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "末将愿往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "磨墨伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上写周瑜三叩首，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "诚惶诚恐奉吴侯：\n空食爵禄数十秋。\n鲁肃可以统貔貅。\n周瑜顿首手书叩。\n甘宁转达奉龙楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "为臣光宠不长久、倘若为臣死之后、甘宁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别都督出帐口，\n披星戴月不停留。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（甘宁下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "鲜血难忍涌出口，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由虎目血泪流。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "吾有一事要恳求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督有何言语吩咐，末将敢不尽心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，列位将军，想吾料难逃生。吾死之后，你们拿住孔明，将他碎尸万段。吾\n在九泉之下，也感众位将军之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "对着众将双叩首，\n拿住孔明报冤仇。\n拜叩主恩谢吴侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天呀，苍天呀！既生瑜尔何生亮，若生亮你莫生瑜。阿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无常一到万事休，气绝咽喉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀都督吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同西皮摇板） 气绝咽喉阴曹走，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可叹英雄万事休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军，都督已死，你我好好看守，等候旨意到来，便知明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理，请。\n众将官，紧守营门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同允，抬周瑜同下。）"
        }
      ],
