    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "你今去把吴营闯",
        "刘备",
        "报子",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周瑜无敌统貔貅，未知狼烟几时休。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "栏江排下千丝网，\n何愁鱼儿不上钩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请坐。吓，先生阴阳，能夺周郎诡计，调遣诸将，四路埋伏，不知胜负，\n先生又命人下书，是何缘故？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公不知：昨晚山人，仰观天象，见将星堕落西地。周郎必去世矣。山人方才\n这封书，正是阎王邀帖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生又来了。他正用谋之时，先生何能定人生死吓？先生此事恍惚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公不信，少时便知明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命下书到吴营，貔貅帐内报军情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀上主公、军师，末将奉命下书于周郎，瑜见此书，呕血而亡。特来启禀主公\n军师知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生预料不错，使孤拜服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀军师：三千岁与众将，俱在巴邱，候军师令下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你先去，少时自有令下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，先生，周瑜亡故，东吴谁人领兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周瑜亡故，东吴并无他人可领，只有鲁肃，为人忠厚，印玺必是他掌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾兵当如何安之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公不晓，亮观天象，将星聚于东方。吾此番要到吴营，假意吊孝为由，往东\n方去访贤士，扶保主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，东吴将士，恨你切骨，又去吊孝，岂不是羊入虎口？不可前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨。周郎在世，亮都不惧，他今已死，又何患乎？山人从巴邱而过，带赵云\n前走，料然无事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，先生吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先生休得自逞强，\n东吴人儿似虎狼。\n怕的失机难提防。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你今去把吴营闯、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "主公但把宽心放，\n山人言来听端详：\n自有妙计暗提防。\n哪怕东吴百万郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先生此去心难放，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "刘备→诸葛亮",
          "turns": 7
        },
        {
          "edge": "诸葛亮→刘备",
          "turns": 8
        },
